      "raw_text": "Secretary Fred CASTOR, Of the\n10000 club, today filed with the\ncity clerk a report Of the recent &C\nton of the club protesting against\nthe proposed franchises asked by\nthe Oregon Railroad & Navigation\nCo. that wants to cross Monroe st.\nThe club asks that date for public\nhearing of the application he set\n\n\nThe county commissioners have\nalready protested against allowing\nthe franchises because the noise\nof the trains passing the court\nhouse will disturb the courts in ses-\nsion."
    }
